{"tid":1799100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經典重溫 批鬥座先係至高無上","createTime":"2019-12-26T16:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T18:40:22.000Z","uid":185731,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2aa3246fb758c7fb15b7d32d6363bffc0b8bf2","tid":1799100,"uid":185731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"批鬥座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會無人敢坐？<br />\n因為任何時間 任何地方， 只要一坐就有機會比人影相放上網批鬥，一坐就係不道德。<br />\n比起任何情緒勒索，自覺不道德先係關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n一坐批鬥座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n你就係不道德，<br />\n同強姦犯/ 殺人犯無分別。<br />\n<br />\n聽起黎好似好恐怖，但係香港人最怕就係依樣。<br />\n<br />\n可能一個咁樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />道德經濟圈係唔健康，但不失為教育既方法。<br />\n<br />\n就算唔係批鬥座 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都會多左人會讓位。"},{"pid":"d32b41627cd323d7d54ba7ce8d04eecbbd15851f","tid":1799100,"uid":185731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:47:12.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"bc5967ea203156a2da6576d503f1c8c6f9b1d18d","tid":1799100,"uid":205339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"入藍店就是批鬥座<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d8335c171a22f2be81c706a6e61c58ac1c0d54","tid":1799100,"uid":185731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"88d5501640ada054d05c05bdce529fd9c74ba352","tid":1799100,"uid":185731,"like":0,"dis